♪ Feelin' big time ♪

1798
02:01:59,958 --> 02:02:02,583
♪ I don't wanna penny pinch
Tryna flip dimes ♪

1799
02:02:02,666 --> 02:02:04,166
♪ What's your life like?
Here's mine ♪

