♪ I'm a fanatic ♪

1805
02:02:16,875 --> 02:02:19,291
♪ Chasin' it, takin' it
Playin' in traffic ♪

1806
02:02:20,041 --> 02:02:21,041
♪ Get it and stack it ♪

1807
