♪ Versace robe
A penthouse at The Ritz ♪

1828
02:04:08,291 --> 02:04:10,458
♪ Rush the paper forth, in inches, blitz ♪

1829
02:04:10,541 --> 02:04:12,541
[singing in Hindi]

1830
02:04:27,458 --> 02:04:29,458
[rapping in Hindi]

1831
02:04:47,041 --> 02:04:48,416
[song ends]

1832
